<div class="post-headline">		<h2>			
			<a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/2014/03/07/a-polished-talk/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Czech Myself Before I Wreck Myself">Czech Myself Before I Wreck Myself</a></h2>
		</div>

<div class="post-bodycopy clearfix"><p>My &#8220;Make Art Not Law&#8221; talk is finally online!<br />
<object width="640" height="360"><param name="movie" value="//www.youtube.com/v/ubZZI67MB8g?hl=en_US&amp;version=3"></param><param name="allowFullScreen" value="true"></param><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always"></param><embed src="//www.youtube.com/v/ubZZI67MB8g?hl=en_US&amp;version=3" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" width="640" height="360" allowscriptaccess="always" allowfullscreen="true"></embed></object></p>
<p>Text and slides <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/2013/12/07/make-art-not-law-2/" target="_blank">here</a>.</p>
