<div class="post-headline">		<h2>			
			<a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/2011/11/11/how-to-free-your-work-video/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to How To Free Your Work video">How To Free Your Work video</a></h2>
		</div>

<div class="post-bodycopy clearfix"><p><iframe src="http://player.vimeo.com/video/30856482" width="500" height="281" frameborder="0" webkitAllowFullScreen allowFullScreen></iframe><br />
Here at last is the video from my first How To Free Your Work workshop, given at NY Foundation for the Arts in Brooklyn, October 5 2011. You can get all the information contained herein as easy-to-read instructions at <a href="http://questioncopyright.org/how_to_free_your_work">QuestionCopyright.org</a>. If you want me to give a workshop like this to your group, please <a href="http://www.ninapaley.com/images/nospam.jpg">contact me</a>.</p>
<div class="plus-one-wrap"><g:plusone href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/2011/11/11/how-to-free-your-work-video/"></g:plusone></div><div class="addtoany_share_save_container"><div class="a2a_kit a2a_kit_size_32 a2a_target addtoany_list" id="wpa2a_15"><a class="a2a_dd addtoany_share_save" href="http://www.addtoany.com/share_save" style="background:url(http://blog.ninapaley.com/wp-content/plugins/add-to-any/favicon.png) no-repeat scroll 4px 0px !important;padding:0 0 0 25px;display:inline-block;height:16px;vertical-align:middle">Share/Bookmark</a></div></div><p class="wp-flattr-button"><a class="FlattrButton" style="display:none;" href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/2011/11/11/how-to-free-your-work-video/" title=" How To Free Your Work video" rev="flattr;uid:ninapaley;language:en_GB;category:text;tags:blog;button:compact;">Here at last is the video from my first How To Free Your Work workshop, given at NY Foundation for the Arts in Brooklyn, October 5 2011. You can get...</a></p></div>

<div class="post-footer">November 11th, 2011 |  Category: <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/advice/" title="View all posts in advice" rel="category tag">advice</a>, <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/archiveorg/" title="View all posts in archive.org" rel="category tag">archive.org</a>, <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/copyleft/" title="View all posts in copyleft" rel="category tag">copyleft</a>, <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/free-culture/" title="View all posts in Free Culture" rel="category tag">Free Culture</a>, <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/new-york/" title="View all posts in New York" rel="category tag">New York</a>, <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/questioncopyrightorg/" title="View all posts in questioncopyright.org" rel="category tag">questioncopyright.org</a>, <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/speaking/" title="View all posts in speaking" rel="category tag">speaking</a>, <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/the-interwebs/" title="View all posts in the interwebs" rel="category tag">the interwebs</a> | <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/2011/11/11/how-to-free-your-work-video/#comments" class="comments-link"  title="Comment on How To Free Your Work video">6 comments</a> </div>
