			<a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/2011/03/29/my-copyright-story-in-a-nutshell/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to My Copyright Story In A Nutshell">My Copyright Story In A Nutshell</a></h2>
		</div>

<div class="post-bodycopy clearfix"><p>This very short, very concise, very understandable article by Rich Bailey is probably the best popular introduction to me and my copyright/copyleft issues. First published by the <a href="http://www.theepochtimes.com/n2/arts-entertainment/filmmaker-nina-paley-freeing-copyright-for-art-and-profit-53342.html">Epoch Times</a>, I re-post it below.</p>
