<p><a href="http://ninapaley.com/mimiandeunice/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/ME_238_AddedValue1.png"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-918" title="ME_238_AddedValue" src="http://ninapaley.com/mimiandeunice/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/ME_238_AddedValue1-640x199.png" alt="" width="640" height="199" /></a></p>
